=== EVENT_VOID_LEVIATHAN ===
# id: 50
# title: Void Leviathan
# chinese_title: 虚空巨兽
# category: AnomalyEncounter
# mode: starmap

A massive creature drifts through the void, its hide covered in crystallized minerals. It seems docile, but its sheer size could crush your ship if startled.

* [[-5 fuel, +35 credits] Carefully mine crystals from its hide]
  ~ fuel_and_credits(-5, 35)
  矿 (kuàng) — mineral
* [[+15 fuel] Siphon residual energy from its wake]
  ~ gain_fuel(15)
  能量 (néngliàng) — energy
* [[Gain crew member] Rescue a trapped pilot in its tendrils]
  ~ gain_crew_member
  救 (jiù) — rescue
* [[Combat level 4] Provoke it and harvest rare materials]
  ~ combat_reward(4, 40)
  战 (zhàn) — battle
* [[Nothing] Give it wide berth and continue]
  ~ nothing
  走 (zǒu) — go, walk
